# Songs API Testing

### 1. Create Song - Valid Request
POST http://localhost:3000/songs HTTP/1.1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Bohemian Rhapsody",
  "artist": ["Queen", "Freddie Mercury"],
  "album": "A Night at the Opera",
  "genre": "Rock",
  "releaseDate": "1975-10-31",
  "duration": "05:55"
}

### 2. Create Song - Another Valid Song
POST http://localhost:3000/songs HTTP/1.1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Imagine",
  "artist": ["John Lennon"],
  "album": "Imagine",
  "genre": "Pop",
  "releaseDate": "1971-09-09",
  "duration": "03:07"
}

### 3. Create Song - Validation Error (Missing Required Fields)
POST http://localhost:3000/songs HTTP/1.1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "",
  "artist": [],
  "album": "Test Album"
}

### 4. Create Song - Invalid Duration Format
POST http://localhost:3000/songs HTTP/1.1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Test Song",
  "artist": ["Test Artist"],
  "album": "Test Album",
  "releaseDate": "2023-01-01",
  "duration": "invalid"
}

### 5. Get All Songs
GET http://localhost:3000/songs HTTP/1.1

### 6. Get Song by ID - Valid
GET http://localhost:3000/songs/2 HTTP/1.1

### 7. Get Song by ID - Not Found
GET http://localhost:3000/songs/999 HTTP/1.1

### 8. Update Song - Full Update (PUT)
PUT http://localhost:3000/songs/1 HTTP/1.1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Bohemian Rhapsody (Remastered)",
  "artist": ["Queen"],
  "album": "A Night at the Opera (Remastered)",
  "genre": "Progressive Rock",
  "releaseDate": "1975-10-31",
  "duration": "05:55"
}

### 9. Update Song - Partial Update (PATCH)
PATCH http://localhost:3000/songs/1 HTTP/1.1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "genre": "Classic Rock"
}

